sequenceDiagram
    participant Parent as Your page<br/>(manual embed)
    participant FacadeAPI as /facade/config<br/>(Wippy BE)
    participant Iframe as iframe.html<br/>(?waitForCustomConfig)

    Parent->>FacadeAPI: GET /facade/config
    FacadeAPI->>Parent: { iframe_url, iframe_origin, ...AppConfig }
    Parent->>Iframe: create &lt;iframe src=iframe_url&gt;
    Note over Parent: addEventListener('message', …)<br/>waiting for the @gen2-chat request
    Iframe->>Parent: postMessage { type:'@gen2-chat', action:'get-config' }
    Parent->>Iframe: postMessage { type:'@gen2-chat', action:'set-config', ...config }<br/>targetOrigin = iframe_origin
    Iframe->>Iframe: initialize with AppConfig (isolated, partial-page)
